<p><a name="Notes" id="Notes"></a></p>
<h2><span class="mw-headline">Notes</span></h2>
<div class="references-small references-column-width" style="-moz-column-width:20em; column-width:20em;">
<ol class="references">
<li id="cite_note-Smil_1991-0"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Smil_1991_0-0" title="">^</a></b> Smil (1991), p. 240</li>
<li id="cite_note-1"><b><a href="#cite_ref-1" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://www.grida.no/climate/ipcc_tar/wg1/041.htm#121" class="external text" title="http://www.grida.no/climate/ipcc_tar/wg1/041.htm#121" rel="nofollow">"Natural Forcing of the Climate System"</a>. Intergovernmental Panel on Climate Change<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.grida.no/climate/ipcc_tar/wg1/041.htm#121" class="external free" title="http://www.grida.no/climate/ipcc_tar/wg1/041.htm#121" rel="nofollow">http://www.grida.no/climate/ipcc_tar/wg1/041.htm#121</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2007-09-29</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Natural+Forcing+of+the+Climate+System&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.pub=Intergovernmental+Panel+on+Climate+Change&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.grida.no%2Fclimate%2Fipcc_tar%2Fwg1%2F041.htm%23121&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Solar_energy"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
